      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works section -->
<section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">How Tramate Works</h2>
    <div class="steps-container">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">Step 1</div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <h3>Create Your Account</h3>
          <p>Sign up to Tramate with your email and connect your Discord account to access your trading signal channels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">Step 2</div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <h3>Connect Exchange</h3>
          <p>Securely connect your Binance account using API keys with carefully limited permissions for your security.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">Step 3</div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <h3>Start Automated Trading</h3>
          <p>Our system automatically executes trades based on signals from your Discord channels, with no manual intervention needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

